In these Regulations—
"the 2018 Act" means the Data Protection Act 2018;
"the GDPR" means Regulation (EU) 2016/679 of the European Parliament and of the Council of 27 April 2016;
"the applied GDPR" has the meaning given by section 21 of the 2018 Act;
"the Commissioner" means the Information Commissioner;
"exit day" has the meaning given by section 20 of the European Union (Withdrawal) Act 2018.
